32\n|match_S\u016aD_EKR=0\u20130\n|match_S\u016aD_FBK=1\u20132\n|match_S\u016aD_\u0160IA=3\u20130\n|match_S\u016aD_\u0160LT=4\u20130\n|match_S\u016aD_V\u0116T=0\u20130\n|match_S\u016aD_\u017dAL=1\u20131\n\n|name_\u0160IA=[[FK \u0160iauliai|\u0160iauliai]]\n|match_\u0160IA_ATL=4\u20134\n|match_\u0160IA_EKR=0\u20135\n|match_\u0160IA_FBK=0\u20130\n|match_\u0160IA_S\u016aD=0\u20132\n|match_\u0160IA_\u0160LT=0\u20131\n|match_\u0160IA_V\u0116T=2\u20130\n|match_\u0160IA_\u017dAL=0\u20132\n\n|name_\u0160LT=[[FK \u0160ilut\u0117|\u0160ilut\u0117]]\n|match_\u0160LT_ATL=1\u20132\n|match_\u0160LT_EKR=0\u20133\n|match_\u0160LT_FBK=1\u20131\n|match_\u0160LT_S\u016aD=1\u20132\n|match_\u0160LT_\u0160IA=2\u20130\n|match_\u0160LT_V\u0116T=0\u20131\n|match_\u0160LT_\u017dAL=1\u20132\n\n|name_V\u0116T=[[FK V\u0117tra|V\u0117tra]]\n|match_V\u0116T_ATL=2\u20131\n|match_V\u0116T_EKR=0\u20132\n|match_V\u0116T_FBK=0\u20132\n|match_V\u0116T_S\u016aD=2\u20130\n|match_V\u0116T_\u0160IA=1\u20130\n|match_V\u0116T_\u0160LT=4\u20130\n|match_V\u0116T_\u017dAL=1\u20130\n\n|name_\u017dAL=[[FK \u017dalgiris|\u017dalgiris]]\n|match_\u017dAL_ATL=5\u20131\n|match_\u017dAL_EKR=0\u20131\n|match_\u017dAL_FBK=1\u20131\n|match_\u017dAL_S\u016aD=2\u20133\n|match_\u017dAL_\u0160IA=2\u20134\n|match_\u017dAL_\u0160LT=0\u20132\n|match_\u017dAL_V\u0116T=1\u20130\n|update=complete\n|source=[http://www2.omnitel.net/almis/ltu08lyga.html www2.omnitel.net] \n}}\n{{col-end}}\n\n{{A Lyga seasons}}\n{{2007\u201308 in European football (UEFA)}}\n{{2008\u201309 in European football (UEFA)}}\n\n[[Category:LFF Lyga seasons]]\n[[Category:2008 in Lithuanian football|1]]\n[[Category:2007\u201308 in European association football leagues|Lith]]\n[[Category:2008\u201309 in European association football leagues|Lith]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football league season\n|season           = 2008\n|dates            = \n|competition      = [[A Lyga]]\n|winners          = <!-- (th title) -->\n|relegated        = \n|continentalcup1  = \n|continentalcup1 qualifiers = \n|continentalcup2  = \n|continentalcup2 qualifiers = \n|continentalcup3  = \n|continentalcup3 qualifiers = \n|league topscorer = \n|biggest home win = \n|biggest away win = \n|highest scoring  = \n|matches          = \n|total goals      = \n|prevseason = [[2007 LFF Lyga|2007]]\n|nextseason = [[2009 A Lyga|2009]]\n|updated    = \n}}\nThe '''Lithuanian [[A Lyga]] 2008''' was the 19th season of top-tier football in Lithuania. The season started on 29 March 2008 and ended on 16 November 2008.\n\nThe league had to reduce the number of its teams from ten to nine prior to this season due to lacking of team able to earn promotion (see below). Shortly before the start of the season, [[FC Vilnius|Vilnius]] withdrew from participating in the league because of unknown reasons, leaving the league with 8 competing teams.\n\n==Clubs==\n{{Location map+|Lithuania|float=right|width=300|caption=Location of teams in the '''A Lyga 2008'''|places=\n{{Location map~|Lithuania|lat=54.9|long=23.933333|label=[[FBK Kaunas|Kaunas]]}}\n{{Location map~|Lithuania|lat=55.7|long=21.133333|label=[[FK Atlantas|Atlantas]]}}\n{{Location map~|Lithuania|lat=54.566667|long=23.35|label=[[FK S\u016bduva Marijampol\u0117|S\u016bduva]]}}\n{{Location map~|Lithuania|lat=55.733333|long=24.35|label=[[FK Ekranas|Ekranas]]}}\n{{Location map~|Lithuania|lat=55.933333|long=23.316667|label=[[FK \u0160iauliai|\u0160iauliai]]}}\n{{Location map~|Lithuania|lat=55.35|long=21.483333|label=[[FK \u0160ilut\u0117|\u0160ilut\u0117]]}}\n{{Location map~|Lithuania|lat=54.683333|long=25.283333|label=[[FK V\u0117tra|V\u0117tra]]<br>[[FK \u017dalgiris Vilnius|\u017dalgiris]]}}\n}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n!Club\n!Location\n!Stadium\n!Capacity\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[FK Atlantas|Atlantas]]||[[Klaip\u0117da]] \n|[[\u017dalgiris Stadium (Klaip\u0117da)|\u017dalgiris Stadium]]\n|5,000\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[FK Ekranas|Ekranas]]||[[Panev\u0117\u017eys]]\n|[[Auk\u0161taitija Stadium]]\n|9,940\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[FBK Kaunas]]||[[Kaunas]]\n|[[S.Dariaus ir S.Gir\u0117no Stadium]]\n|8,500\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[FK S\u016bduva Marijampol\u0117|S\u016bduva]]||[[Marijampol\u0117]]\n|[[S\u016bduva stadium|S\u016bduva Stadium]]\n|4,000\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[FK \u0160iauliai|\u0160iauliai]]||[[\u0160iauliai]]\n|[[Savivaldyb\u0117 Stadium]]\n|2,430\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[FK \u0160ilut\u0117|\u0160ilut\u0117]]||[[\u0160ilut\u0117]]\n|[[\u0160ilut\u0117 Stadium]]\n|3,000\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[FK V\u0117tra|V\u0117tra]]||[[Vilnius]]\n|[[V\u0117tra Stadium]]\n|5,900\n|-\n|style=\"text-align:left;\"|[[FK \u017dalgiris Vilnius|\u017dalgiris]]||[[Vilnius]]\n|[[\u017dalgiris Stadium]]\n|15,030\n|}\n\n==Promotion and relegation==\n[[Interas-AE Visaginas]] were relegated to the [[Lithuanian First League]] after finishing the [[2007 LFF Lyga|2007 season]] in last place with only 8 points. [[FK \u0160ilut\u0117|\u0160ilut\u0117]] were originally scheduled to play the 2nd placed team of the First League, [[Rodiklis Kaunas]], in a relegation play-off, but Rodiklis declined promotion due to lacking financial capabilities.\n\nFirst League champions [[Alytis Alytus]] also had to forfeit their place in this year's league because their ground was not suitable for top-tier football, so no team was promoted.\n\n==Standings==\n<onlyinclude>{{#invoke:sports table|main|style=WDL\n|show_limit=5\n|res_col_header=QR\n|sortable_table=y\n\n|team1=EKR|name_EKR=[[FK Ekranas|Ekranas]]\n|team2=FBK|name_FBK=[[FBK Kaunas]]\n|team3=V\u0116T|name_V\u0116T=[[FK V\u0117tra|V\u0117tra]]\n|team4=S\u016aD|name_S\u016aD=[[FK S\u016bduva Marijampol\u0117|S\u016bduva]]\n|team5=\u017dAL|name_\u017dAL=[[FK \u017dalgiris|\u017dalgiris]]\n|team6=ATL|name_ATL=[[FK Atlantas|Atlantas]]\n|team7=\u0160IA|name_\u0160IA=[[FK \u0160iauliai|\u0160iauliai]]\n|team8=\u0160LT|name_\u0160LT=[[FK \u0160ilut\u0117|\u0160ilut\u0117]]\n|win_EKR=20|draw_EKR=5|loss_EKR=3|gf_EKR=46|ga_EKR=12|status_EKR=C\n|win_FBK=16|draw_FBK=7|loss_FBK=5|gf_FBK=51|ga_FBK=17\n|win_V\u0116T=14|draw_V\u0116T=6|loss_V\u0116T=8|gf_V\u0116T=33|ga_V\u0116T=24\n|win_S\u016aD=14|draw_S\u016aD=6|loss_S\u016aD=8|gf_S\u016aD=35|ga_S\u016aD=25\n|win_\u017dAL=6|draw_\u017dAL=10|loss_\u017dAL=12|gf_\u017dAL=27|ga_\u017dAL=41\n|win_ATL=7|draw_ATL=7|loss_ATL=14|gf_ATL=31|ga_ATL=44\n|win_\u0160IA=5|draw_\u0160IA=9|loss_\u0160IA=14|gf_\u0160IA=24|ga_\u0160IA=41\n|win_\u0160LT=3|draw_\u0160LT=4|loss_\u0160LT=21|gf_\u0160LT=19|ga_\u0160LT=62|status_\u0160LT=R\n|hth_V\u0116T=VET: 7 pts, 5\u20133; SUD: 4 pts, 3\u20135\n|hth_S\u016aD=V\u0116T\n|hth_\u017dAL=\u017dAL: 5 pts, 7\u20136; ATL: 5 pts, 6\u20137\n|hth_ATL=\u017dAL\n|col_CL2=green1|text_CL2=[[2009\u201310 UEFA Champions League#Second qualifying round|2009\u201310 UEFA Champions League Second qualifying round]]\n|result1=CL2\n|col_EL2=blue1|text_EL2=[[2009\u201310 UEFA Europa League#Second qualifying round|2009\u201310 UEFA Europa League Second qualifying round]]\n|result2=EL2\n|col_EL1=blue2|text_EL1=[[2009\u201310 UEFA Europa League#First qualifying round|2009\u201310 UEFA Europa League First qualifying round]]\n|result3=EL1\n|col_EL2b=blue1|text_EL2b=[[2009\u201310 UEFA Europa League#Second qualifying round|2009\u201310 UEFA Europa League Second qualifying round]] \n|note_res_EL2b=[[FK S\u016bduva Marijampol\u0117|S\u016bduva]] won the [[2008\u201309 Lithuanian Football Cup]] and thereby qualified for the [[2009\u201310 UEFA Europa League#Second qualifying round|second qualifying round]] of the UEFA Europa League.\n|result4=EL2b\n|col_R=red1|text_R=Relegation to [[2009 1 Lyga]]\n|result8=R\n\n|update=complete\n|source=[http://www2.omnitel.net/almis/ltu08lyga.html www2.omnitel.net] \n|class_rules=1) points; 2) head-to-head points; 3) head-to-head goal difference; 4) head-to-head goals scored; 5) goal difference; 6) number of goals scored.\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Results==\nEvery team played each other four times, twice at home and twice on the road, for a total of 28 games.\n\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===First half of season===\n\n{{#invoke:Sports results|main\n|matches_style=FBR|solid_cell=grey\n|team1=ATL|team2=EKR|team3=FBK|team4=S\u016aD|team5=\u0160IA\n|team6=\u0160LT|team7=V\u0116T|team8=\u017dAL\n\n|name_ATL=[[FK Atlantas|Atlantas]]\n|match_ATL_EKR=1\u20131\n|match_ATL_FBK=1\u20131\n|match_ATL_S\u016aD=0\u20131\n|match_ATL_\u0160IA=0\u20131\n|match_ATL_\u0160LT=2\u20130\n|match_ATL_V\u0116T=1\u20130\n|match_ATL_\u017dAL=2\u20132\n\n|name_EKR=[[FK Ekranas|Ekranas]]\n|match_EKR_ATL=1\u20130\n|match_EKR_FBK=1\u20130\n|match_EKR_S\u016aD=1\u20130\n|match_EKR_\u0160IA=1\u20130\n|match_EKR_\u0160LT=4\u20130\n|match_EKR_V\u0116T=1\u20131\n|match_EKR_\u017dAL=1\u20130\n\n|name_FBK=[[FBK Kaunas]]\n|match_FBK_ATL=4\u20130\n|match_FBK_EKR=0\u20133\n|match_FBK_S\u016aD=3\u20130\n|match_FBK_\u0160IA=2\u20130\n|match_FBK_\u0160LT=3\u20130\n|match_FBK_V\u0116T=1\u20132\n|match_FBK_\u017dAL=2\u20130\n\n|name_S\u016aD=[[FK S\u016bduva Marijampol\u0117|S\u016bduva]]\n|match_S\u016aD_ATL=3\u20131\n|match_S\u016aD_EKR=2\u20131\n|match_S\u016aD_FBK=0\u20130\n|match_S\u016aD_\u0160IA=1\u20130\n|match_S\u016aD_\u0160LT=2\u20131\n|match_S\u016aD_V\u0116T=3\u20130\n|match_S\u016aD_\u017dAL=0\u20130\n\n|name_\u0160IA=[[FK \u0160iauliai|\u0160iauliai]]\n|match_\u0160IA_ATL=1\u20131\n|match_\u0160IA_EKR=0\u20132\n|match_\u0160IA_FBK=0\u20130\n|match_\u0160IA_S\u016aD=0\u20131\n|match_\u0160IA_\u0160LT=3\u20130\n|match_\u0160IA_V\u0116T=0\u20132\n|match_\u0160IA_\u017dAL=1\u20131\n\n|name_\u0160LT=[[FK \u0160ilut\u0117|\u0160ilut\u0117]]\n|match_\u0160LT_ATL=2\u20134\n|match_\u0160LT_EKR=0\u20131\n|match_\u0160LT_FBK=0\u20136\n|match_\u0160LT_S\u016aD=1\u20131\n|match_\u0160LT_\u0160IA=2\u20132\n|match_\u0160LT_V\u0116T=1\u20133\n|match_\u0160LT_\u017dAL=0\u20132\n\n|name_V\u0116T=[[FK V\u0117tra|V\u0117tra]]\n|match_V\u0116T_ATL=0\u20130\n|matc