 Sopoaga]].\n\n===Undrafted free agents===\nAll [[Undrafted sportsperson|undrafted free agent]]s were signed just after the [[2014 NFL draft]] concluded on April 30, 2014.<ref>{{cite news|last1=Staff|first1=CSN|title=REPORT: PATRIOTS SIGN NINE UNDRAFTED FREE AGENTS|url=http://www.csnne.com/new-england-patriots/report-patriots-sign-nine-undrafted-free-agents|accessdate=January 16, 2017|publisher=CSNNE.com|date=May 1, 2016}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|New England Patriots|border=2}}\"|Position \n! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|New England Patriots|border=2}}\"|Player \n! style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|New England Patriots|border=2}}\"|College\n|-\n| [[Cornerback|CB]] || style=\"background:#ADD8E6 | [[Malcolm Butler]] || [[West Alabama Tigers football|West Alabama]]\n|-\n\n|}\n{|class=wikitable\n|-\n| style=\"background:#ADD8E6; width:20px; em;\"| \n| Made regular season roster\n|}\n\n==Staff==\n{{NFL final staff\n|Year=2014\n|TeamName=New England Patriots\n|Front Office=\n*Chairman/CEO \u2013 [[Robert Kraft]]\n*President \u2013 [[Jonathan Kraft]]\n*Director of Player Personnel \u2013 [[Nick Caserio]]\n*Director of College Scouting \u2013 [[Monti Ossenfort]]\n*Director of Pro Scouting \u2013 [[Bob Quinn (American football)|Bob Quinn]]\n*Football Research Director \u2013 [[Ernie Adams (American football)|Ernie Adams]]\n*Assistant to the Coaching Staff \u2013 [[Michael Lombardi (American football)|Michael Lombardi]]\n|Head Coaches=\n*Head Coach/Director of Football Operations/General Manager \u2013 [[Bill Belichick]]\n|Offensive Coaches=\n*Offensive Coordinator/Quarterbacks \u2013 [[Josh McDaniels]]\n*Running Backs \u2013 [[Ivan Fears]]\n*Wide Receivers \u2013 [[Chad O'Shea]]\n*Tight Ends \u2013 [[Brian Daboll]]\n*Offensive Line \u2013 [[Dave DeGuglielmo]]\n|Defensive Coaches=\n*Defensive Coordinator \u2013 [[Matt Patricia]]\n*Linebackers \u2013 [[Patrick Graham (American football)|Patrick Graham]]\n*Cornerbacks \