u02bfIr\u0101q wa-sh-Sh\u0101m}}''\n| war = the [[Iraq War]] (2003\u20132011), the [[Iraqi insurgency (2011\u201313)|Iraqi insurgency]], the [[Syrian Civil War]], the [[Iraqi Civil War (2014\u20132017)|Iraqi Civil War]], the [[Libyan Civil War (2014\u2013present)|Second Libyan Civil War]], the [[Boko Haram insurgency]], the [[War in North-West Pakistan]], the [[War in Afghanistan (2015\u2013present)|War in Afghanistan]], the [[Yemeni Civil War (2015\u2013present)|Yemeni Civil War]], and [[List of wars and battles involving ISIL|other conflicts]]\n----\nPrimary target of [[Operation Inherent Resolve]] and of the [[military intervention against ISIL]] [[American-led intervention in Syria|in Syria]], [[American-led intervention in Iraq (2014\u2013present)|Iraq]], [[2015 Egyptian military intervention in Libya|Libya]], and [[Boko Haram insurgency|Nigeria]]<!-- for wikilinks, if diff from name -->\n|image = {{multiple image\n | border = infobox\n | total_width = 320\n | image_gap = 20\n | caption_align = center\n | image1 = AQMI Flag asymmetric.svg{{!}}border\n | caption1 = The [[Black Standard]] used by ISIL<ref>{{cite news |first=Kashmira |last=Gander |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/isis-flag-what-do-the-words-mean-and-what-are-its-origins-10369601.html |title=Isis flag: What do the words mean and what are its origins? |date=7 July 2015 |work=[[The Independent]]}}</ref>\n | image2 = ISIL_Caliphate_Seal.svg\n | caption2 = The seal of ISIL<ref>{{cite web|url=https://jihadology.net/2019/01/29/new-video-message-from-the-islamic-state-fulfilling-the-promise-wilayat-al-iraq-kirkuk/|title=New video message from The Islamic State: \"Fulfilling the Promise \u2013 Wil\u0101yat al-'Ir\u0101q, Kirk\u016bk\"|first=Aaron Y.|last=Zelin|date=29 January 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Statement of ISIS \u2013 The Battle of Brussels |url=https://www.investigativeproject.org/pics/large/1419.jpg |website=Investigativeproject.org |language=ar}}</ref><ref>{{cite